estealth</A> <small></small> </a><br></div> <small><i>reply to <A rel='nofollow' HREF="/forum/r28816441-">thestealth</A></i></small><br><p> Thank you for the feedback. I'll give the TSP a try and take it from there.</TD></TR><TR><TD style="border-top: 0px;" VALIGN=BOTTOM BGCOLOR=#FFFFFF HEIGHT=20><div class="cmd-links" style="text-align:right; line-height:30px;"><small><A rel='nofollow' href='javascript:;' style="cursor:pointer;" onClick="inlineajax('/speak/vote/28817618?ajh=1&enc=64urlL2ZvcnVtL3IyODgxNjQ0MS1FbnZpcm9ubWVudGFsLUNsZWFuaW5nLWEtaGVhdnktc21va2VyLXMtaG91c2UjMjg4MTc2MTg', 'qr28817618'); return false;">actions</a> &middot; <font color=#808080>2013-Nov-15 3:56 pm</font> &middot; <form action="/speak/remark,28817618?enc=64urlL2ZvcnVtL3IyODgxNjQ0MS1FbnZpcm9ubWVudGFsLUNsZWFuaW5nLWEtaGVhdnktc21va2VyLXMtaG91c2UjMjg4MTc2MTg" method="post"><input type=submit value="reply" style="font-size: smaller;"></form> </small></div><div style="display:none; border-top: 1px dashed #CCCCCC" id="qr28817618"></div></TD></TR><TR><TD VALIGN=TOP ROWSPAN=2 WIDTH=140 class="uinfo " BGCOLOR=#EEEEEE><IMG SRC="http://i.dslr.net/1ptrans.gif" HEIGHT=1 WIDTH=140><br><A name=28817826> </A><div style="text-align:center;"><A HREF="/profile/270506"><b>goldfinger</b></A><br><small><br>join:2000-12-24<br>00000</small></div><small></small></small></TD><TD data-rmid="28817826" data-uid="270506" VALIGN=TOP BGCOLOR=#EEEEEE WIDTH=100% style="border-bottom: 0px;"><div class="uinfo_small " style="display:none;"><a href="/profile/270506"> <A HREF="/profile/270506">goldfinger</A> <small></small> </a><br></div> <small><i>reply to <A rel='nofollow' HREF="/forum/r28816441-">thestealth</A></i></small><br><p> I will 3rd the TSP others have mentioned.  We purchased a house in 2010 that was previously owned by heavy smoker.  It was so bad after going through with the Realtor my nose burned all night! I was expecting to have to deal with the smoke smell forever.  We washed the walls / doors / cabinets with TSP. Then painted all surfaces with 2 coats of Killz.  Shampooed the carpet. I thought we'd never get rid of the smell completely, but it was gone in a couple days.</TD></TR><TR><TD style="border-top: 0px;" VALIGN=BOTTOM BGCOLOR=#EEEEEE HEIGHT=20><div class="cmd-links" style="text-align:right; line-height:30px;"><small><A rel='nofollow' href='javascript:;' style="cursor:pointer;" onClick="inlineajax('/speak/vote/28817826?ajh=1&enc=64urlL2ZvcnVtL3IyODgxNjQ0MS1FbnZpcm9ubWVudGFsLUNsZWFuaW5nLWEtaGVhdnktc21va2VyLXMtaG91c2UjMjg4MTc4MjY', 'qr28817826'); return false;">actions</a> &middot; <font color=#808080>2013-Nov-15 5:11 pm</font> &middot; <form action="/speak/remark,28817826?enc=64urlL2ZvcnVtL3IyODgxNjQ0MS1FbnZpcm9ubWVudGFsLUNsZWFuaW5nLWEtaGVhdnktc21va2VyLXMtaG91c2UjMjg4MTc4MjY" method="post"><input type=submit value="reply" style="font-size: smaller;"></form> </small></div><div style="display:none; border-top: 1px dashed #CCCCCC" id="qr28817826"></div></TD></TR><TR><TD VALIGN=TOP ROWSPAN=2 WIDTH=140 class="uinfo " BGCOLOR=#FFFFFF><IMG SRC="http://i.dslr.net/1ptrans.gif" HEIGHT=1 WIDTH=140><br><A name=28817948> </A><div style="text-align:center;"><A HREF="/profile/1524524"><b>Mr Matt</b></A><br><small><br>join:2008-01-29<br>Eustis, FL<br>kudos:1</small></div><small><b>Reviews:</b><br><IMG SRC="http://i.dslr.net/v2/WIRELESS14.gif" WIDTH=14 HEIGHT=14 class="txtb">&middot;<A HREF="/comment/3165/80647">Millenicom</A><br><IMG SRC="http://i.dslr.net/v2/ISP14.gif" WIDTH=14 HEIGHT=14 class="txtb">&middot;<A HREF="/comment/1566/73153">Embarq Now Centu..</A><br><IMG SRC="http://i.dslr.net/v2/CABLE14.gif" WIDTH=14 HEIGHT=14 class="txtb">&middot;<A HREF="/comment/1579/67069">Comcast</A><br><IMG SRC="http://i.dslr.net/v2/ISP14.gif" WIDTH=14 HEIGHT=14 class="txtb">&middot;<A HREF="/comment/1519/84076">CenturyLink</A><br></small></small></TD><TD data-rmid="28817948" data-uid="1524524" VALIGN=TOP BGCOLOR=#FFFFFF WIDTH=100% style="border-bottom: 0px;"><div class="uinfo_small " style="displa